  3.809968073566992*^9, 3.8099681536568317`*^9}, {3.810557260250428*^9, 
  3.8105572606139913`*^9}, {3.8130835305386977`*^9, 3.8130836194514275`*^9}, {
  3.918582359889065*^9, 3.9185823608158913`*^9}, {3.937486311831871*^9, 
  3.9374863121315765`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"09cbb332-bde9-46eb-9567-\
dce2a6a09bb3"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Shown in Figure 10.1 is such a potential energy surface for a diatomic \
molecule, where two nuclei are separated by a distance ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"\[LeftBracketingBar]", 
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["R", "2"], "-", 
     SubscriptBox["R", "1"]}], "\[RightBracketingBar]"}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"78b89345-6d45-43fa-b0b9-7d8f01a828e0"],
 ". Each point along the potential is the solution to the electronic \
component of the Schr\[ODoubleDot]dinger equation with fixed nuclear \
coordinates,"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8130829090107307`*^9, 3.8130829343887296`*^9}, {
  3.9185823629348755`*^9, 3.918582571617481*^9}, {3.937493113226284*^9, 
  3.9374931138298435`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f73149b4-9b55-4f40-81ad-\
00961b4fe9fe"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox[
    OverscriptBox[
     StyleBox["H",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
    StyleBox["e",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", 
    StyleBox["e",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    RowBox[{
     StyleBox["r",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], ";", 
     StyleBox["R",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox[
    StyleBox["E",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox["e",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", 
    StyleBox["e",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    RowBox[{
     StyleBox["r",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], ";", 
     StyleBox["R",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.81307809350165*^9, 3.8130781609264364`*^9}, 
   3.8130782039890594`*^9, {3.813078272672757*^9, 3.8130783323990836`*^9}, {
   3.8130788081537347`*^9, 3.8130788107416773`*^9}, {3.813082960788761*^9, 
   3.8130829717709465`*^9}, {3.8130830114286995`*^9, 
   3.8130830511844254`*^9}, {3.813083923369066*^9, 3.813083930891937*^9}, {
   3.8132222114766717`*^9, 3.8132222127335887`*^9}, {3.8132271828852577`*^9, 
   3.8132271927822623`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1f98f937-0999-4a74-8ab6-\
fd797725dc05"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "where the value of the potential is given by ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  SubscriptBox[
   StyleBox["E",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], 
   StyleBox["e",
    FontSlant->"Italic"]]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.81307809350165*^9, 3.8130781609264364`*^9}, 
    3.8130782039890594`*^9, {3.813078272672757*^9, 3.8130783323990836`*^9}, {
    3.8130788081537347`*^9, 3.8130788107416773`*^9}, {3.813082960788761*^9, 
    3.8130829717709465`*^9}, {3.8130830114286995`*^9, 
    3.8130830511844254`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "10769e50-02fe-40fa-bc56-5dd32d43cc81"],
 ". Here the semicolon is used to note that the position of the nuclei is \
fixed in this calculation. The portion of the Hamiltonian that acts on the \
electronic wavefunction is given by"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8130830535436316`*^9, 3.813083082807993*^9}, 
   3.813083625886711*^9, {3.8130837815577264`*^9, 3.813083812857699*^9}, {
   3.918582591116088*^9, 
   3.9185826144119368`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"94bda8e8-95c7-462a-9c70-\
39a9821aca4d"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  SubscriptBox[
   OverscriptBox[
    StyleBox["H",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
   StyleBox["e",
    FontSlant->"Italic"]], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox[
     OverscriptBox[
      StyleBox["T",
       FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
     StyleBox["e",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     StyleBox["r",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], 
     StyleBox[")",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], "+", 
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox[
     OverscriptBox[
      StyleBox["V",
       FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
     StyleBox["eN",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     RowBox[{
      StyleBox["r",
       FontSlant->"Italic"], 
      StyleBox[",",
       FontSlant->"Plain"], 
      StyleBox["R",
       FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
     StyleBox[")",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], "+", 
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox[
     OverscriptBox[
      StyleBox["V",
       FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
     StyleBox["ee",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     StyleBox["r",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], 
     StyleBox[")",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], "+", 
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox[
     OverscriptBox[
      StyleBox["V",
       FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
     StyleBox["NN",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     StyleBox["R",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], 
     StyleBox[")",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8130759614135423`*^9, 3.813076278147323*^9}, {
   3.813076380382406*^9, 3.8130764153085423`*^9}, 3.813076816633875*^9, {
   3.8130771563624783`*^9, 3.8130771828803873`*^9}, {3.8130838177067156`*^9, 
   3.8130838358785024`*^9}, {3.8132254458791065`*^9, 
   3.813225446255906*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e963fa81-356e-4592-a4af-\
da1a70cc0342"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Note that sometimes the term ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox[
    OverscriptBox[
     StyleBox["V",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
    StyleBox["NN",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    StyleBox["R",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.8130759614135423`*^9, 3.813076278147323*^9}, {
    3.813076380382406*^9, 3.8130764153085423`*^9}, 3.813076816633875*^9, {
    3.8130771563624783`*^9, 3.8130771828803873`*^9}, {3.8130838177067156`*^9, 
    3.8130838358785024`*^9}, {3.8132254458791065`*^9, 3.813225446255906*^9}},
  ExpressionUUID->"104c6963-07ea-49b7-84c4-b5f955d362d4"],
 "is not included at this point because it only shifts the electronic \
energies by a fixed amount. We still need to find a way to solve for the \
nuclear positions and nuclear energy. If we now look back at our full \
Hamiltonian using our approximate wavefunction,"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.813221862635882*^9, 3.813221941736092*^9}, 
   3.813222056973484*^9, {3.813222111720174*^9, 3.8132221286298065`*^9}, {
   3.8132223872654524`*^9, 3.8132223981117973`*^9}, {3.813223370548111*^9, 
   3.813223416530096*^9}, {3.813225462052038*^9, 
   3.813225488511286*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"27107bc8-bdb4-4cf1-9d5b-\
47839502121c"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"[", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox[
       OverscriptBox[
        StyleBox["T",
         FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
       StyleBox["N",
        FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
      RowBox[{"(", 
       StyleBox["R",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], 
       StyleBox[")",
        FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox[
       OverscriptBox[
        StyleBox["T",
         FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
       StyleBox["e",
        FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
      RowBox[{"(", 
       StyleBox["r",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], 
       StyleBox[")",
        FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox[
       OverscriptBox[
        StyleBox["V",
         FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
       StyleBox["eN",
        FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
      RowBox[{"(", 
       RowBox[{
        StyleBox["r",
         FontSlant->"Italic"], 
        StyleBox[",",
         FontSlant->"Plain"], 
        StyleBox["R",
         FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
       StyleBox[")",
        FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox[
       OverscriptBox[
        StyleBox["V",
         FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
       StyleBox["NN",
        FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
      RowBox[{"(", 
       StyleBox["R",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], 
       StyleBox[")",
        FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox[
       OverscriptBox[
        StyleBox["V",
         FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
       StyleBox["ee",
        FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
      RowBox[{"(", 
       StyleBox["r",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], 
       StyleBox[")",
        FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}]}], 
    StyleBox["]",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
   SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", 
    StyleBox["N",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    StyleBox["R",
     FontWeight->"Bold",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
   SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", 
    StyleBox["e",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    RowBox[{
     StyleBox["r",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], ";", " ", 
     StyleBox["R",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox[
    StyleBox["E",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox["tot",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", 
    StyleBox["N",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    StyleBox["R",
     FontWeight->"Bold",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
   SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", 
    StyleBox["e",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    RowBox[{
     StyleBox["r",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], ";", " ", 
     StyleBox["R",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8132221669142685`*^9, 3.8132221794693403`*^9}, {
  3.8132222690385857`*^9, 3.813222292552426*^9}, {3.8132271998127046`*^9, 
  3.8132272188847957`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"cd7e4d76-cbe1-4588-ab5b-\
c9859b9b06b6"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "we would like to be able to write this equation with two separable terms \
for the energy, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  SubscriptBox[
   StyleBox["E",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], 
   StyleBox["e",
    FontSlant->"Italic"]]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.81307809350165*^9, 3.8130781609264364`*^9}, 
    3.8130782039890594`*^9, {3.813078272672757*^9, 3.8130783323990836`*^9}, {
    3.8130788081537347`*^9, 3.8130788107416773`*^9}, {3.813082960788761*^9, 
    3.8130829717709465`*^9}, {3.8130830114286995`*^9, 
    3.8130830511844254`*^9}, {3.813083923369066*^9, 3.813083930891937*^9}, {
    3.8132222114766717`*^9, 3.8132222127335887`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "120ac57a-bd97-4d64-b004-5131d9602484"],
 " and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  SubscriptBox[
   StyleBox["E",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], 
   StyleBox["N",
    FontSlant->"Italic"]]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.8132221669142685`*^9, 3.8132221794693403`*^9}, {
   3.8132222690385857`*^9, 3.813222292552426*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "954959ac-0ce1-49bf-ac31-81612a457389"],
 ", representing the electronic and nuclear contributions to the energy, \
respectively. The total energy is then given by ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox[
    StyleBox["E",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox["tot",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], "=", 
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox[
     StyleBox["E",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], 
     StyleBox["e",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]], "+", 
    SubscriptBox[
     StyleBox["E",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], 
     StyleBox["N",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]]}]}]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.8132221669142685`*^9, 3.8132221794693403`*^9}, {
   3.8132222690385857`*^9, 3.813222292552426*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "2efbe311-821f-4cb1-b728-9159c4a3de58"],
 ". "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8132223004640656`*^9, 3.8132223573761525`*^9}, {
   3.8132224154592094`*^9, 3.8132224350207834`*^9}, {3.8132224858087974`*^9, 
   3.813222489210738*^9}, {3.8132226453566236`*^9, 3.8132227144611435`*^9}, 
   3.813222844490904*^9, {3.918582845452071*^9, 
   3.9185828467813587`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"80006e20-a0ed-4af6-a45e-\
5b06635f6e0f"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "To separate the terms, we have to make sure that the operators don\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]t act on both components, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", 
    StyleBox["N",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    StyleBox["R",
     FontWeight->"Bold",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.8132221669142685`*^9, 3.8132221794693403`*^9}, {
   3.8132222690385857`*^9, 3.813222292552426*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "2a9011e4-67da-4aed-b356-688dea400a0f"],
 "and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", 
    StyleBox["e",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    RowBox[{
     StyleBox["r",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], ";", " ", 
     StyleBox["R",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.8132221669142685`*^9, 3.8132221794693403`*^9}, {
   3.8132222690385857`*^9, 3.813222292552426*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "288490ae-17fb-49a9-b6b2-ad9f6de0ae03"],
 ". The kinetic energy operator for the electrons, "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8132230408699813`*^9, 3.813223097845091*^9}, {
   3.8132231293068175`*^9, 3.813223129308816*^9}, {3.91858290865811*^9, 
   3.9185829105142217`*^9}, {3.918582943038615*^9, 3.9185829661418285`*^9}, 
   3.91858303639534*^9, 3.9185831993910103`*^9, 
   3.9374864165635643`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"f6608c9c-f6be-454e-9337-\
863b3251f49b"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox[
    OverscriptBox[
     StyleBox["T",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
    StyleBox["e",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    StyleBox["r",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], "=", 
  RowBox[{"-", 
   RowBox[{
    UnderscriptBox["\[Sum]", 
     StyleBox["i",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
    RowBox[{
     FractionBox["1", "2"], 
     SubsuperscriptBox["\[Del]", 
      StyleBox["i",
       FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"]}]}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8130765928719873`*^9, 3.8130766419857407`*^9}, {
   3.813076783365462*^9, 3.813076786478775*^9}, 3.81307681962652*^9, {
   3.813076858567613*^9, 
   3.8130768586821976`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ee23484d-dc2f-8f46-a8d6-\
4a30d2a81c33"],

Cell["does not depend on the nuclei, so we can write", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.813222867032816*^9, 3.8132228934419155`*^9}, {
  3.876386865645952*^9, 
  3.876386867681657*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5d64549e-4936-d342-9391-\
d02763010eac"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox[
    OverscriptBox[
     StyleBox["T",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
    StyleBox["e",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    StyleBox["r",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
   SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", 
    StyleBox["N",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    StyleBox["R",
     FontWeight->"Bold",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
   SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", 
    StyleBox["e",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    RowBox[{
     StyleBox["r",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], ";", " ", 
     StyleBox["R",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", 
    StyleBox["N",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    StyleBox["R",
     FontWeight->"Bold",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
   SubscriptBox[
    OverscriptBox[
     StyleBox["T",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
    StyleBox["e",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    StyleBox["r",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
   SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", 
    StyleBox["e",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    RowBox[{
     StyleBox["r",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], ";", " ", 
     StyleBox["R",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8132221669142685`*^9, 3.8132221794693403`*^9}, {
  3.8132222690385857`*^9, 3.813222292552426*^9}, {3.8132228964605904`*^9, 
  3.8132229086113567`*^9}, {3.813227228896858*^9, 
  3.813227230620051*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"371dcc44-3729-ca43-8415-\
a134ae7dc347"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "However, since both ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", 
    StyleBox["N",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    StyleBox["R",
     FontWeight->"Bold",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.8132221669142685`*^9, 3.8132221794693403`*^9}, {
   3.8132222690385857`*^9, 3.813222292552426*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "25195bc4-c9da-4f43-a8cb-28f4fbd4e59e"],
 "and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox["\[Phi]", 
    StyleBox["e",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    RowBox[{
     StyleBox["r",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], ",", 
     StyleBox["R",
      FontWeight->"Bold",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
    StyleBox[")",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.8132221669142685`*^9, 3.8132221794693403`*^9}, {
   3.8132222690385857`*^9, 3.813222292552426*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "b8f8c47f-bc09-4d41-80ad-a549e843288c"],
 "depend on ",
 StyleBox["R",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ", the same statement does not apply to the kinetic energy operator for the \
nuclei,"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8132229132506676`*^9, 3.813222981389715*^9}, {
  3.8132235205277023`*^9, 
  3.8132235227097645`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"87dd7af4-61e0-454c-a5a0-\
