7e8280f66e66"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "However, it turns out that the magnitude of the correction due to \
dependence on both portions is very small (see ",
 ButtonBox["Sherrill",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["http://vergil.chemistry.gatech.edu/notes/quantrev/quantrev.pdf"], 
    None},
  ButtonNote->
   "http://vergil.chemistry.gatech.edu/notes/quantrev/quantrev.pdf"],
 " 7.2), so we can to good approximation write "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8132230408699813`*^9, 3.813223097845091*^9}, {
  3.8132231293068175`*^9, 
  3.813223129308816*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8535e598-67e0-414d-ab3b-\
48fbe49de1da"],

