Cell["\<\
that we saw in the Fock operator for multielectron atoms in Lesson 08. The \
equivalent operator for molecules is\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.813500849617487*^9, 3.813500921188555*^9}, {
  3.813500984778073*^9, 3.813500989345745*^9}, {3.9375734602941246`*^9, 
