     "\"\<\!\(\*StyleBox[\"R\",FontSlant->\"Italic\"]\)\!\(\*StyleBox[\"/\",\
FontSlant->\"Italic\"]\)\!\(\*SubscriptBox[StyleBox[\"a\",FontSlant->\"Italic\
\"], \"0\"]\)\>\"", ",", 
      "\"\<\[CapitalDelta]\!\(\*StyleBox[\"E\",FontSlant->\"Italic\"]\)\!\(\*\
StyleBox[\" \
